# PERFORMANCE GUARD

While generating advanced UI:

Ensure the site remains performant.

Follow rules:

Animations
• use requestAnimationFrame
• avoid layout thrashing
• avoid excessive DOM nodes

Scroll effects
• throttle using rAF
• use IntersectionObserver when possible

CSS
• prefer transforms over top/left
• avoid heavy box shadows on large lists

JavaScript
• modular functions
• minimal global variables

Always include:

• reduced-motion fallbacks
• mobile optimizations
• lazy loading for heavy effects